snippet.title: Equalicious
snippet.description:
Download from here!
 - http://bit.ly/29tbQzv

Do you know how much is 1+1? Then, you already know how to play Equalicious!

Discover the permutasty, pitagoric and fibonastic puzzles of Equalicious!

Train your brain going through its multiple levels, sorting the tiles to resolve simple equations with basic operations, but, don’t be fooled!

Join your friends in this fantastic adventure. Find them along the way through different fantastic and mathematical worlds in 3D.
Help them to advance and challenge them to become the Emperor of Mathematics.
